Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:41.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}那個約定的小山上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:50.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}月光之下吻著鮮豔欲滴的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}那把鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:58.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}通向不思議之國度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:03.22,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}緊緊攥著它的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:07.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}無法長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:14.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}沒有什麼值得害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:22.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}你絕不是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:32.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}我會立刻來到你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:36.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}無論你在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:39.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}我們都緊緊相連
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.22,0:24:49.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,500)\be0}我會立刻將你緊緊擁抱
