Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是不是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼神靈們會這麼慌亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在害怕  被同伴孤立了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺比之前看到時小了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要帶上它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡…匡幸  武器  武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不行  不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據氣象局預報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風11號正位於津島西南方120公里\N海洋面以時速70公里迅速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心區域保持著最大風速40米的強勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果照這樣登錄北九州  與過去的颱風10號…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  這邊也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…抱歉  那邊也能幫我弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  連慧都過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的颱風好像很厲害啊  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊不要緊  男人變多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨對我們來說到是有利的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神會救我們之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那個宗教團體最近強迫水天鎮一個女孩成為了新教祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個教祖說  最近龍神會降臨到這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  衣服的尺寸我回去改一下  一會兒穿起來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去準備自己的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平田醫生  要搭我的車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事必須向古森你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理診療  是為了我的研究而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼  憎惡和記憶的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為扁桃體和海馬體間的系統存在缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我想古森會不會是第一個克服這種缺陷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療我很認真  但動機不純
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是多虧了醫生您而精神起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且醫生來到這邊後  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想弄清楚我腦中的異變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:05:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環境對腦產生的影響  這是我的新目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你讓我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我在聽這些錄音時見到了古森的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然這是意識變異的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姐姐對那時的古森說了一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幽世和夢裡都沒能見到姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這一定有什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一定有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  如果是古森一定能救出都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做這點小事  很抱歉其他的都幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是水天鎮宗教法人  大神拜靈會的門口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據村民們的證言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該團體的代表  竟然是一位小學生的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能聚集這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工生命體…都死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種說法真不像你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培養素都清理乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但計劃的流水線上還是製造了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是初期  但實驗性的生產已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照上面的指示  應該會作暫時的廢棄處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中島先生  雖然不該我說  但能請你去把你太太接回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸他很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請看  在水天町的田地之間架起了無數的鳥居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民們真的相信龍神會降臨這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我確實也對大神大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但原則上是政教分離的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  鈴木大叔可真能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  已經過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道男  就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  等一會兒會把你帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  已經來了嗎  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在此時  有一位身穿和服像母親的女性帶著一個小女孩打算進入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  這不是很合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定行  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  別笑啦  多對不起太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算進得去  之後才是關鍵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的神靈開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我不知道創造生命是否是允許人類進行的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果沒有這種覺悟就動手  會變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人類創造的你們也是我們的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊也被媒體纏住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…加畑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  在現世看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從葛城過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照一言主神的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這孩子來侍奉大神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但請你們改日再來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能突然潛進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那我跟道男就來佯動作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神什麼的不會出現啦  對吧  阿榮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好大  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？好像能看見什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…  龍神  是龍神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神  龍神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  是龍神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神  龍神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…龍…龍神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎麼了  明明什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得太過分了吧  道男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  你不能留在這裡  跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駒玖珠先生已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在鈴木先生去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  快點  都不能待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神出現了  如大神大人所言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再也感覺不到悲傷和厭惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實沒有我的存在會更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都就是都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是其他任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千帆  別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個男孩進了大神大人的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從玄關進入正面突破會不會太難？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面就沒有逃走的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可以逃走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去內房  關禁閉時我曾被關在裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能打架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是同伴  你只是跟大家稍有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…龍神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裡有一個茶箱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就已經挖好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們的祖先想用這個暗道做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一片漆黑什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒關係對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在讓大神大人被帶走  好像不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  找機會逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就應該乖乖聽大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面清楚的留著你的指紋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個殺死了那個男人會怎麼樣  你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法  那就要教育一下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們晚了點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能等待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我多點勇氣  那孩子也不會遇到這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼  榆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  你們是同伴  好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不會被同伴孤立了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  都  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  別再逞強了  你我都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微嚇嚇他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道男呀  你都幹了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我都那麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的  騙你的  成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是大神大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:21:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能再見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在幽世守護著太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠了  就算你不那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐跟我成為一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐跟我成為一體  現在也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像都最初把我看成光  我也確實感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.75,0:24:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}信  你也來笑一個
